snippet.title: My Time at Sandrock - Cinematic Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
My Time at Sandrock is coming to Nintendo Switch this summer! Wishlist today: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/my-time-at-sandrock-switch/

Travel to the desert community of Sandrock and take on the role of a fledgling Builder. Use your trusty toolset to gather resources, construct machines, and turn your run-down workshop into a well-oiled production facility to save the town from the jaws of economic ruin!

#MyTimeAtSandrock #IndieWorld #NintendoSwitch

Subscribe for more Nintendo fun! https://goo.gl/HYYsot

Visit Nintendo.com for all the latest! http://www.nintendo.com/
